name: UW Spring Show 2019 Lineup Reveal
description:
Spring Show 2019 is right around the corner, and we know you’ve been dying to find out the lineup… help Dubs head to HUB Lawn in order to unlock the artists!

Spring Show 2019 presented by ASUW Arts + Entertainment 

Location: HUB Lawn 

Date: May 17th, 2019

Time: 5 PM 

*Free w/ UW ID*

RSVP on the Spring Show 2019 FB Event Page to look out for more details!

More info about ASUW A+E at:

Website: arts.asuw.org    IG: asuwae  Twitter: asuw_ae    Facebook: asuw.ae
